byline.original: By SUSANNE CRAIG and BEN PROTESS

abstract: While many on Wall Street are withholding support from President Obama for now, Warren E. Buffett has agreed to headline two fund-raisers.
snippet: While many on Wall Street are withholding support from President Obama for now, Warren E. Buffett has agreed to headline two fund-raisers.
lead_paragraph: When it comes to business, everyone on Wall Street wants a piece ofWarren E. Buffett. His presidential politics, however, appear to be another matter altogether.

headline.main: Others Go, but Buffett Stays on President's Side
